This paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML) applied to text analysis. The paper focuses on improving the effectiveness of news headlines through keyword identification and ranking, as well as predicting shareability on social media. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses supervised regression models, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and the tool is designed to combine automated predictors with human judgments, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
